div.div: The second season of Princess Connect! Re:Dive.

A sci-fi, summer story filled with suspense set on a small island with Shinpei Aijiro, whose childhood friend Ushio Kofune died. He returns to his hometown for the first time in two years for the funeral. Sou Hishigata, his best friend, suspects something's off with Ushio's death, and that someone can die next.
A sinister omen is heard as an entire family next door suddenly disappears the following day. Furthermore, Mio implicates a "shadow" three days before Ushio's death.
(Source: Disney+)

After a disastrous defeat at the 2018 World Cup, Japan's team struggles to regroup. But what's missing? An absolute Ace Striker, who can guide them to the win. The Japan Football Union is hell-bent on creating a striker who hungers for goals and thirsts for victory, and who can be the decisive instrument in turning around a losing match...and to do so, they've gathered 300 of Japan's best and brightest youth players. Who will emerge to lead the team...and will they be able to out-muscle and out-ego everyone who stands in their way? (Source: Kodansha USA) Note: Winner of the 45th Kodansha Manga Award in the Shounen Category in 2021.

At school, Kyouko Hori is known for being smart, attractive, and popular. On the other hand, her classmate, the boring, gloomy Izumi Miyamura tends to get painted as a "loser fanboy." But when a liberally pierced and tattooed (not to mention downright gorgeous) Miyamura appears unexpectedly on the doorstep of secretly plain-Jane homebody Hori, these two similarly dissimilar teenagers discover that there are multiple sides to every story...and person! (Source: Yen Press) Note: Includes 20 extra chapters.

div.span: Turbulent Adventurers are Introverted, Observant, Feeling, Prospecting and Turbulent. Adventurers are flexible and charming, always ready to explore and experience something new. They tend to have open minds, approaching life, new experiences, and people with grounded warmth.
Mostly Introverted. Likely prefers fewer, yet deep and meaningful, social interactions and feels drawn to calmer environments.
Mostly Observant. Likely pragmatic and down-to-earth, with a strong focus on what is happening or very likely to happen.
Mostly Feeling. Likely values emotional expression and sensitivity, prioritizing empathy, social harmony, and cooperation.
Mostly Prospecting. Likely very good at improvising and adapting. Tends to be flexible and values novelty above stability.
Mostly Turbulent. Likely self-conscious, sensitive to stress, success-driven, perfectionistic, and eager to improve.
